        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-lg p-8 text-center border-2 border-blue-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">âœ…</div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2 text-lg">Sertifikasi Halal</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Produk halal dan aman tersertifikasi oleh LPPOM MUI</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-lg p-8 text-center border-2 border-blue-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ğŸ·ï¸</div>
